sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as AccountOwner
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant UserCtrl as UserController
participant UserSvc as UserService
participant Redis as RedisProfileCache
participant UserDb as MongoUserProfile
User->>Client: Xem profile cua toi
Client->>Gateway: GET /api/users/me
Gateway->>UserCtrl: getCurrentUser
UserCtrl->>UserSvc: resolve actor from context
UserSvc->>Redis: GET user:<userId>
alt Cache hit
  UserSvc-->>Client: profile from cache
else Cache miss
  UserSvc->>UserDb: find profile
  UserSvc->>Redis: SET cache
  UserSvc-->>Client: profile from DB
end
User->>Client: Cap nhat profile
Client->>Gateway: PUT/PATCH /api/users/:userId
Gateway->>UserCtrl: updateUserProfile
alt userId == actorId
  UserSvc->>UserDb: update fields
  UserSvc-->>Client: 200
else Co gang sua profile nguoi khac
  UserSvc-->>Client: 403 forbidden
end
